<FILEID>AP-NR-02-11-89 1223EST</FILEID>
<FIRST>r i AM-SAfrica-HungerStrike     02-11 0509</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-SAfrica-Hunger Strike,0524</SECOND>
<HEAD>Government Bans Meetings Planned in Support of Hunger Strikers</HEAD>
<HEAD>EDS: Retransmitting a0537 to restore cycle designator.</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By DAVID CRARY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>JOHANNESBURG, South Africa (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Human rights activists Saturday
threatened defiance and warned of rising black anger after police
